stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> intake
    intake --> scoping : start_scope (echo: emit ingest topology; Recall seeds the first directive)
    intake --> ingesting : start_ingest [constraints.ingest_branches]
    scoping --> ingesting : scope_done (model-emitted topology → dynamic fan;\n3-focus default = tagged LOAN fallback when scoping emits nothing)
    ingesting --> designing : ingest_done (parallel echo fan-in, bounded by max_fan_width)
    designing --> charter_gate : design_done
    charter_gate --> authoring : approve
    charter_gate --> designing : refine
    charter_gate --> error : deny
    authoring --> authoring : author_next (per lesson)
    authoring --> assessing : author_done
    assessing --> assessing : assess_next (per lesson)
    assessing --> synthesizing : assess_done
    synthesizing --> verifying : synth_done
    verifying --> critiquing : verify_clean (EVIDENCE-GATED: recomputation transcripts required)
    verifying --> fixing : verify_fix (budget)
    verifying --> complete : verify_exhausted (met=False)
    fixing --> verifying : fix_done (always re-verify, whole corpus)
    critiquing --> complete : critique_pass (APPROVE)
    critiquing --> fixing : critique_fix (budget)
    critiquing --> complete : critique_exhausted (met=False)

    scoping --> unknown : UNCERTAIN / needs_clarification / no-valid-topology (loan ablated)
    ingesting --> unknown : UNCERTAIN / needs_clarification
    designing --> unknown
    authoring --> unknown
    assessing --> unknown
    synthesizing --> unknown
    verifying --> unknown : stalled violations
    fixing --> unknown
    critiquing --> unknown
    unknown --> awaiting_clarification : escalate
    awaiting_clarification --> designing : clarify (lesson progress preserved)

    intake --> error : abort
    scoping --> error : abort
    ingesting --> error : abort
    designing --> error : abort
    charter_gate --> error : abort
    authoring --> error : abort
    assessing --> error : abort
    synthesizing --> error : abort
    verifying --> error : abort
    fixing --> error : abort
    critiquing --> error : abort
    unknown --> error : abort
    awaiting_clarification --> error : abort

    complete --> [*]
    error --> [*]
